videos.description: Andrew Wiggins gets an offensive rebound and finds Taj Gibson who finishes with a flush while the exuberant crowd chants the Vikings' rally cry "Skol."
videos.headline: Skol chant inspires Wolves

videos.description: Karl-Anthony Towns fakes out the defender then quickly kicks it out to Taj Gibson who finishes with the flush.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Towns drops perfect pass to Gibson) 2018/01/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Towns drops perfect pass to Gibson

videos.description: Jamal Crawford drains a long 3-pointer to give the Timberwolves a 12-0 run in the 2nd quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Crawford's long 3-pointer extends Wolves run) 2018/01/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Crawford's long 3-pointer extends Wolves run

videos.description: The Wolves force a turnover and Andrew Wiggins gets a perfect pass to Jimmy Butler who throws it down.

videos.headline: Wiggins finds Butler for the slam
